Syntax: private_coffer [deposit || balance || transfer] [amount]

Displays the status of the clan private coffer, or makes
a deposit to the coffer. This coffer is used by the clan
leaders to purchase improvements for the clan, such as
additional rooms for the clan hall.

If no argument, or an argument of 'balance' is given, the current
balance will be displayed.

If an argument of 'deposit' is given, 'amount' will be deducted from
your coins and put into the coffer.

If an argument of 'transfer' is given, 'amount' will be deducted from
your bank account and put into the coffer.
